VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT urllib\.request\.urlopen\s*\(|urllib\.urlopen\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:request\.|input\(|argv|\+ && MISSING:allowlist|whitelist|urlparse|is_private
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects urllib-based outbound requests potentially influenced by user input.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for SSRF: urllib with User-Controlled URL.
